headline: Wedbush upgrades Pulte to 'outperform' as it sees stock undervalued
summary: Investing.com -- Wedbush upgraded PulteGroup Inc (NYSE:PHM) to "outperform" from "neutral" given an overdone stock price decline and strong catalysts for growth. Shares were up 2.1% at $110.
